{
  "stem": "11144.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she opened the door from it, and all of a sudden she saw some people in there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it turned out that it was like a potato-- not a dump, potato--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like a potato cellar.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when she opened it, there were some people already hidden in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she pushed me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She pushed my sister in there, and she jumped in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And while we were there, we found out from the other people, too, that the aktion was going on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that they-- and we would-- we stayed there in that cellar with our hearts on our shoulders, I have to tell you, because we heard everything that was going on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We heard the Germans passing back and forth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we heard the squeaking and the screeching and the yelling and the-- and the German language and shooting and-- and all that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And luckily, I don't know what happened, that some other people opened the door.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some other people came in and were saved with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we stayed there until the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the middle of the night, thanks to the other people that were there, because my mother wouldn't have any idea where to go or what to do, we came out from there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were not far from the Bug, from the River Bug.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in the middle of the night, we crossed that River Bug.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I guess my mother had probably held my sister somehow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Thank god that the river was not really that deep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And me, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Somebody probably-- maybe there was a young man there or whatever-- took me on his shoulders and crossed the River Bug.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When we crossed the River Bug, we ended up in the forest.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
